short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Create a klusternetes k8s cluster from your browser

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Klusternetes offers instant self-service Kubernetes clusters, enabling engineers to spend less time spinning up clusters, and more time focusing on the essential tasks. Klusternetes.com and our CLI enable us to provide this and more integrations with pipelines.

This extension is another quick way of provisioning a Klusternetes cluster using your existing accounts from the web application.
